verbose_text: These results are not surprising, given that the only 2 trials identified to measure the change in prevalence of overweight and obesity among children in this review, those by Sichieri et al. XREF_BIBR and James et al., XREF_BIBR focused on a single message that included reducing soda consumption, which may have been insufficient to limit excessive weight gain.
